name: Has Your Dream Of Dating A Cute Bunny Girl Finally Come True?
name_original: Has Your Dream Of Dating A Cute Bunny Girl Finally Come True?
description:
A little game created for the O2A2 2022 game jam!

Story

You got hit by a truck and it hurts like hell, but things may be okay after all because you wake up and find a... bunny girl?

Features
  • Like, a ton of endings. Mostly bad though.
  • A cute bunny girl!
